@startuml level2_four_agents
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundCorner 10

title **Level 2 — Four Agents (Core Roles)**

|Client|
start
:Submit business question;

|#E3F2FD|Engagement Manager|
:Decompose question into\nworkstreams & sub-questions;
:Create analysis plan;
note right
  **Model:** qwen3:8b (Ollama)
  **Tools:** none (structured decomposition)
  **Cannot:** research, analyze, write report
end note

|#E8F5E9|Market Researcher|
:Receive analysis plan;
:Investigate market landscape;
:Produce structured findings\n(competitors, trends, segments);
note right
  **Model:** qwen3:14b (Ollama)
  **Tools:** search_web(), read_document()
end note

|#F3E5F5|Strategy Consultant|
:Receive market findings;
:Synthesize into recommendation;
:Write final consulting report\nwith options & tradeoffs;
note right
  **Model:** qwen3:32b (Ollama)
  **Tools:** reads all prior analyses from context
  **Cannot:** search for new info
end note

|#FFFDE7|Evaluator|
:Score report on rubric\n(completeness, accuracy, coherence,\nstructure, actionability, critical depth);
:Produce evaluation scorecard;
note right
  **Model:** gemini-2.5-flash (Google AI Studio)
  **Tools:** none — reads report from context
end note

|Client|
:Receive report + evaluation;
stop

@enduml
